Soljaks are a collection of 6969 pixelated characters on the Solana Blockchain.

We want to create a healthy community that not only supports each other when down and spreads joy throughout the crypto space. 

Community is very important to us and we want everybody feels like they can have a say in the direction that this project takes. Also, the art is CC0 - holders own the art so feel free to monetise it however you like.

We can’t wait to have you on this journey with us.
